Package project3

Class Management

java.lang.Object
project3.Employee
project3.Fulltime
project3.Management
public class Management
extends Fulltime
Management class is an extension of the Fulltime class. It is for managerial employees and holds a managers title.
Author:
Shane Hoffman, Michael Li
